{"tid":55051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[生炒骨]成日諗住一個叫過既hg算唔算沉船?","createTime":"2016-12-26T05:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T06:35:49.000Z","uid":69937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60dfa7358094f031f23f08a7832aba4bd91dd846","tid":55051,"uid":69937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"巴打當我鳩嗡又好當笑話睇又好啦<br />\n因為真係唔知同邊個講好<br />\n小弟雞齡都有接近6年<br />\n但因為我係毒撚既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧願俾貴啲都唔想俾人見到<br />\n所以多數都係搵hg (hotel girls)<br />\n最近發覺忘記唔到早幾年遇到既一個好正既hg<br />\n<br />\n當時啱啱出黎做嘢<br />\n搵到錢就叫雞破左青頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁叫開梗係有鋪癮啦<br />\n果陣hg仲係7，800蚊一次<br />\n差唔多一個月都去兩，三次<br />\n開頭食黎食去既都係普通既質素<br />\n食完唔會番食果啲<br />\n有次連肥婆都食埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個唔識彈人鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果時已經知啲agent p相p得好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時上到去完全唔同人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者p到成個外星人咁 <br />\n一睇就知有伏果啲<br />\n但係就見到有條女啲身材好正<br />\n見agent啲廣告又話<br />\n21歲 身高173 38F內衣模特兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個樣仲幾靚<br />\n咁無理由唔試架<br />\n<br />\n點知上到去<br />\n條女真係咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又後生 問佢話91年出世 <br />\n無錯 果陣係2012，2011左右<br />\n真係17x左右高<br />\n對波堅大 真係有F cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要好挺唔墜<br />\n好似沖田杏梨咁<br />\n係膚色無白 可能係燈光問題<br />\n暈又細 淺啡色<br />\n差唔多走肥無腩咁滯<br />\n唯一你地可能挑剔就係佢粒lin唔突<br />\n有一邊仲直情笠左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且果陣佢係著低胸t-shirt加熱褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係果啲令人性欲大減既支那性感睡衣<br />\n露出更深既事業線同一對長腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n性格又健談又豪放<br />\n除除下衫拉你跳下舞<br />\n又肯配合<br />\n未試過乳交既我就梗係想試下啦<br />\n難得見到咁大波<br />\n佢好似有少少抗拒<br />\n但都肯照幫我夾<br />\n不過佢唔識夾<br />\n又無落油<br />\n所以唔太爽<br />\n但係我果陣又緊張得滯<br />\n事關第一次同咁正既女做<br />\n夾幾夾就出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射左好多上佢對波到<br />\n時間唔長但好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁完事沖完涼都傾左陣計<br />\n問佢有無接過細過我既客<br />\n佢話接過個7+8歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係太快射 但佢免費俾多次佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得以佢性格 佢真係會<br />\n果陣即刻後悔點解成日打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為長期打飛機既關係<br />\n果陣我射完一次要回好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咁正我梗係唔止食一次啦<br />\n第二次上到去<br />\n比上次更加熱情<br />\n做咩果啲唔詳細講啦<br />\n唔識寫甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完事話想影佢相<br />\n佢都俾<br />\n又識擺晒pose<br />\n我真係覺得佢係內衣model<br />\n最後仲合照左幾張<br />\n不過果陣部手機跌左落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無back up<br />\n<br />\n我就淨係搵左佢兩次<br />\n無其他巴打咁多錢<br />\n可以日日搵女女一次<br />\n所以都係佢黎一次我搵一次<br />\n後來聽講佢2012後半已經去左新加坡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢兩年先搵番果邊啲post<br />\n評論都係話佢身材好驚人<br />\n但好似服務無我果陣咁好了<br />\n仲開始有肚腩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都無阻我想搵佢既念頭<br />\n但發現最後一個post係2013年了<br />\n<br />\n故事就到呢到<br />\n想問巴打有無印象見過個差唔多既hg<br />\n想了解多啲佢 我好似真係沉左船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢果陣叫FS.EE"},{"pid":"0d4d5dfb36568388278921918d4fa1b547f62c34","tid":55051,"uid":69937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}